{"tid":794872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"找錯錢會唔會比返收銀員","createTime":"2018-08-26T14:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T16:08:04.000Z","uid":80706,"like":12,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec9819aba0ad5e955c9a679801e21db35a95f52","tid":794872,"uid":80706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"話說今日喺Ok入錢落八達通，畀咗張500蚊 同個收銀話講入500，嘟完睇埋餘額諗住走啦 ，個收銀好快咁畀張500蚊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後即刻收下個客啲錢<br />\n我猶豫咗陣，最後都係畀返啲錢收銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家諗返都係覺得有啲掙扎，諗緊當時應唔應該畀返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係你會唔會畀返啲錢收銀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔畀 佢找錯錢係佢on9 點解要畀返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀返 人吔都係打份工啫 攞咗啲錢人哋都自己畀返 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c711ffb12025caba7c2612aeb1fd110cdc7ef4e","tid":794872,"uid":80706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9435695c272b4978748aa3eddf1770724b29cb22","tid":794872,"uid":82482,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"咁就乖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee56e7215dc519c31572de8bd41bd449b0edc87","tid":794872,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"500蚊姐"},{"pid":"a7a5fc7b7b9b3c2f1aef3aa5be0c703c7369f5fc","tid":794872,"uid":147780,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"我都試過類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去找換店兌錢，俾咗幾千蚊港紙個職員<br />\n佢將果幾千蚊夾埋喺我要兌嘅錢入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有掙扎過，但諗人哋要填翻條數可能白做成個星期工，最後我都翻轉頭俾翻人"},{"pid":"9e614ee361e08b815b8e3f3648198ba96352f0a6","tid":794872,"uid":80706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a7a5fc7b7b9b3c2f1aef3aa5be0c703c7369f5fc","tid":794872,"uid":147780,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"我都試過類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去找換店兌錢，俾咗幾千蚊港紙個職員<br />\n佢將果幾千蚊夾埋喺我要兌嘅錢入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有掙扎過，但諗人哋要填翻條數可能白做成個星期工，最後我都翻轉頭俾翻人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"唔少巴打都會畀返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊唔少人都話唔會畀返 <br />\n話當自己賺咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0607f51ebd88a5229b3b53705dae357b5dc36dd","tid":794872,"uid":147780,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e614ee361e08b815b8e3f3648198ba96352f0a6","tid":794872,"uid":80706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a7a5fc7b7b9b3c2f1aef3aa5be0c703c7369f5fc","tid":794872,"uid":147780,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"我都試過類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去找換店兌錢，俾咗幾千蚊港紙個職員<br />\n佢將果幾千蚊夾埋喺我要兌嘅錢入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有掙扎過，但諗人哋要填翻條數可能白做成個星期工，最後我都翻轉頭俾翻人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"唔少巴打都會畀返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊唔少人都話唔會畀返 <br />\n話當自己賺咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"我身邊有啲朋友都係咁諗<br />\n覺得唔係偷唔係搶，係個職員塞俾你點解唔要<img src=\"/assets/face